    {
        "content": "<p>Take <code>M := Bool</code> with multiplication given by <code>||</code> and one given by <code>false</code>, with the order <code>a &lt; b ↔ a = false ∧ b = true</code>, and whose topology is <code>⊤</code></p>",
        "id": 512162317,
        "sender_full_name": "Aaron Liu",
        "timestamp": 1744660559
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/find/?pattern=SupConvergenceClass#doc\">docs#SupConvergenceClass</a> provides a lower estimate on <code>inst : TopologicalSpace M</code>, thus you can take <code>\\top</code> as topology on any nontrivial ordered monoid <code>M</code> and get a counterexample.</p>",
        "id": 512171660,
        "sender_full_name": "Yury G. Kudryashov",
        "timestamp": 1744664125
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Semi-offtopic: <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"816344\">@Aaron Liu</span> fixed <code>CoeTC.coe</code> in this file in <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/24047\">#24047</a>. I'm fixing the other file using <code>CoeTC.coe</code> in <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/24051\">#24051</a>. It would be nice if someone fixes <code>Coe.coe</code>, see <a href=\"https://loogle.lean-lang.org/?q=Coe.coe\">https://loogle.lean-lang.org/?q=Coe.coe</a> too. I won't have time for this today and tomorrow.</p>",
